quickly.name: quickly
quickly.title: Transition Quickly
quickly.description: Use this design token for a quick transition. Most often used for quick hover effects on things such as links, icons and more.

slowly.name: slowly
slowly.title: Transition Slowly
slowly.description: Use this design token for a slow transition. Used for example in modals, tooltips, collapsing elements, and more.

mobile.name: mobile
mobile.title: Transition Mobile
mobile.description: Use this design token for mobile menu transitions. Used for example in the mobile version of popout and dropdown.
